# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo, regardless of the OS or editor
# that wrote them. Without this, a tool that rewrites files with CRLF endings
# produces a whole-repo phantom diff. Binary assets are excluded so git never
# tries to "fix" their line endings.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.pdf binary
